---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <div class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-5 md:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">About</h1>
      <div class="max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-8">
          ProductBuildersHQ provides frameworks and case studies for the evolution of product development in the age of AI.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-4">
          We believe the boundaries between Product Managers and Engineers are dissolving. AI is compressing implementation barriers, shifting value toward specification, validation, and operational ownership.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
          Our frameworks help individuals and teams navigate this transition, whether you are a PM learning to build, an Engineer developing product judgment, or an organization evolving toward higher autonomy levels.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">What We Publish</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
          <li><strong class="text-[var(--color-text)]">Frameworks:</strong> Maturity models with levels, tools, metrics, and practices for growth.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-[var(--color-text)]">Case Studies:</strong> Real-world implementations from companies like AWS, Spotify, and StrongDM.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Living Documents</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
          Our frameworks are living documents, updated quarterly as tools evolve and new patterns emerge. Each document includes version numbers and update dates for transparency.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
          Have feedback on our frameworks? Found a case study we should cover? Reach out on
          <a href="https://github.com/ProductBuildersHQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline">GitHub</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
